21 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Surety bail bond premium -- fees or interest. A surety bail bond
22 producer that collects any fees or interest other than the minimum premium shall disclose the fees or interest at
23 the time the surety bail bond insurance contract is executed. All fees and interest must be acknowledged by all
24 parties to the contract.
25
26 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Codification instruction. [Section 3] is intended to be codified as an
27 integral part of Title 33, chapter 26, part 1, and the provisions of Title 33, chapter 26, part 1, apply to [section 3].
